  }, "Financial Valentine\u2019s Day"), mdx("p", null, "It was February 14th, 2020, and instead of flowers or a box of chocolates, I dealt with finances. It turned out that a year of entrepreneurship had a positive effect on me. I handled everything myself \u2014 promptly and efficiently. They were amazed at me in the new bank. They gave me a list of things they needed from me, and I brought them the papers back in a few hours. \u201CMr. Z\xE1hradn\xEDk, are you on vacation? No, I\u2019m an entrepreneur. Now I need to deal with this, so I\u2019m dealing with it. There\u2019s no point in doing anything else.\u201D"), mdx("div", {
