2019m the one with the harm. For each additional day, when the contract is active, I pay fees. However, I decided to leave it at that. It is a damage of about 24 euros, and I no longer want to run around the branches for them. I will earn them faster elsewhere."), mdx("p", null, "The lady is signing a new notice agreement with today\u2019s date, and I make sure that the account number where they will pay me any balance will already be in my other bank. I sign and hope that this chapter will close soon. But I\u2019ll keep an eye on it \u2014 word of mouth on their part is no longer enough for me."), mdx("p", null, "I say, \u201CWell, we\u2019ve solved this part. I would now like to cancel my account, complete with everything. I don\u2019t use it.\u201D The lady tells me, \u201CSir, but it\u2019s not just like that. The request goes to this department, and they will offer you a beneficial product, a free account.\u201D"), mdx("p", null, "\u2014 They\u2019ve already called me. I don\u2019t pay for the account, but I don\u2019t use it. I want to cancel it."), mdx("p", null, "\u2014 I see that the offer is valid until August 31. Until then, it cannot be canceled just like that."), mdx("p", null, "\u2014 Are you telling me that I can\u2019t cancel my account before this deadline?"), mdx("p", null, "\u2014 Of course, you can. But you know, I\u2019m going to have to call headquarters again."), mdx("p", null, "It seems to me as if the lady is complaining about having to do her job. Eventually, however, she calls there. \u201CYes, the gentleman wants to cancel the account. He has a promo deal now, but he has already decided\u2026\u201D"), mdx("p", null, "\u2014 So, Mr. Z\xE1hradn\xEDk, we can cancel the account, but I have noticed that you still have an active investment account."), mdx("p", null, "\u2014 Excuse me? It was paid a long time ago."), mdx("p", null, "\u2014 Yes, but it\u2019s still active on the system. We need to deactivate it before we can cancel your personal 